title: Federico Franchini
text:
Federico Franchini (born 23 January 1994) is an Italian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="A.S.D.%20Villafranca">Villafranca</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Serie%20C">Serie C</a> debut for <a href="A.C.%20Lumezzane">Lumezzane</a> on 1 September 2013 in a game against <a href="F.C.%20Pro%20Vercelli%201892">Pro Vercelli</a>.
